      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to experience a fantastic ride! This vehicle is in good condition, reflecting the consistent care and maintenance it has received. It handles beautifully on the road and maintains a sharp appearance, making it a reliable and stylish choice for your next adventure. Don't miss out on this well-kept gem!",
      "price": 38500.0,
