      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the driver who values a synthesis of proven reliability and refined performance. Demonstrating consistent mechanical care and a sophisticated road presence, this offering provides exceptional utility and operational excellence. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that remains steadfast in its delivery of both comfort and long-term value.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    }
